{"tid":2173974,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【制裁前攞錢】鄭若驊持股安樂工程 美國附屬獲最多7,800萬貸款補助","createTime":"2020-08-25T14:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T14:57:00.000Z","uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2732d6efcc7b1977d2f9aeecb03858e6a249167","tid":2173974,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"美國薪酬保障計劃Paycheck Protection Program（PPP）貸款計劃，由4月3日推出至本月初到期，當地更準備推出新一輪PPP計劃。雖然中美關係緊張，但有關計劃資助企業名單中，卻不乏港股以至中資企業，近日被美國制裁的律政司司長鄭若驊，其與丈夫潘樂陶持有63%的安樂工程（1977），旗下美國附屬公司TEI，亦取得貸款，金額更達到上限1,000萬美元（約7,800萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200826/5F5JPKCCHFGW7IJRTAWY6JICFU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200826%2F5F5JPKCCHFGW7IJRTAWY6JICFU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=9c022fb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200826%2F5F5JPKCCHFGW7IJRTAWY6JICFU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=82b27adb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200826/5F5JPKCCHFGW7IJRTAWY6JICFU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9d86ae94fd5475b9bd7bb4749eb495cc9ca63684","tid":2173974,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c902fe1e7a677149994cc5524b3624d111650f","tid":2173974,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"攞咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" cl